docker image bulid is the most important of all things in manaagina a docker

1.docker image bulid is creating a virtual environment for the application to run

2.the main important thing of a docker container is pid 1
3.pid 1 is the main process runs inside the container we start the container
4.blindly we a bulid a apache image and  runing it,exposing will not give you the output because the main process apache is not running
5.in orderd to get the output from the container we need to start the apache service in the container at start time 
6.this can be achieved by CMD or ENTRYPOINT.sh
